
Reverse Proxy Docker Container
==============================

Overview
--------

       Web browser
            |
  https://192.168.33.20:10443/
            |
            V  port:443
      +------------+
      |    Nginx   |
      +------------+
            |
  http://192.168.33.21:8080/
            |
            V
    Application Server


Files
-----

- README
- docker-compose.yml
- nginx.conf
- ssl/
  - server.key 
  - server.crt

Usage
-----

sudo docker-compose up -d
